name: Memories
description:
H.Y.E Story

Have you ever felt bored with the things that are happening to you right now?
Sometimes I feel tired, because I've done the same thing over and over again. When I reflect, I remember my past when I was a child. During those days I always played with my friends, cycled, and laughed together. Those times were very beautiful when I didn't think about worldly problems. That's why I made a device where I can relive my past. But my project was terminated by the government because I used illegal materials. now it's left with my old memories replaying.
